value.0: Hello there, dear! What can I do for you?
Perhaps you have need of an experienced cleric? I promise I will do my best to keep you in excellent health. You will gain the talents of one who can heal and fight in exchange for some of the loot.
Goddess speed your journey and keep you safe. If you have need of my skills, I shall be here, unless I join up with someone else.
I am sorry, my dear, but you already have someone with you. Are you sure you still need my help?
Of course. If you are alone and still need my help, I will be here.
<StartCheck>[Failure]</Start> I am sorry. If you are by yourself, then I will gladly join up with you.
<StartCheck>[Success]</Start> Of course, dear. For you, anything. Lead the way.
You will not regret this, dear <FirstName>. I am at your service.
It is wonderful to see you again, dear. Have you a need of me?
Hello there, dear. What can I do for you?
Oh, my friend, is this true? Are you you sure this is what you want?
Then let us continue, dear.
Then I shall wait at the Trade of Blades until you have further need of me again. Please don't be long.
Hello dear. I trust everything is well with you.

value.0: I... don't have the senses of some damnable thief... but I do think that there is danger here.
I'll be going now.
I could use a good cleric. Welcome to the team, Linu.
Fine. Forget I asked.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Please, I need all the help I can get on my mission.
Never mind.
I think we need to part ways.
No, never mind.
I'm sure.
I'd like to buy off some of the loot that you picked up.
